      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1414///blog.ericchen.name/post/41ec7a20-d1c5-4cfe-b27f-8604a0a8e670/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;簡介&#34;&gt;簡介&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;header-anchor&#34; href=&#34;#%e7%b0%a1%e4%bb%8b&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theregister.com/2024/02/16/what_is_unix/&#34; title=&#34;Forgetting the history of Unix is coding us into a corner&#34; rel=&#34;noopener external nofollow noreferrer&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; class=&#34; exturl&#34;&gt;&#xA;    Forgetting the history of Unix is coding us into a corner&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa fa-external-link-alt&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;FOSDEM 2024 的演講，從 UNIX 歷史來講解 Everything is a File 的概念，蠻詳細的，對每一個時代的 UNIX 都有介紹&lt;/p&gt;</description>
